            <div style="text-align:center;"><div style="font-size:24px;line-height:1;">🛠️</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:#475569;margin-top:3px;">Tools</div><div style="font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:#B45309;">5</div></div>
